\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 How many years older than you was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Oh, he was - he seventy odd I couldn't t
ell you how old he was when I was born I only remember him when I got older you see - few years older and I - latter part of my years I remember - remember him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 He died when he was seventy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 He died when he was seventy - yes, seventy - seventy-o
ne. And then my sister died, she died - the next one to - to - to him, Margaret, she was sixty-four when she died. She had strokes. And then - like - before my elder brother died, my sister other sister died, the one that he was - that was thirty-three bu
t
 I'm not quite sure whether she was the - she was the second eldest I think. She was the second eldest, the one that died at thirty-three. You see and then - then - my eldest sister died after my brother and then - my - other sister died. She was sixty-fo
ur. But it wasn't long in between each other you see. In between us - the last four about two years in between you see. Well near enough to years anyway.
