ied in about 1913 - I should think about - between 19 - 1912 to '13 - either - one of those two years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Did you say he was fifty-six when he died?
