n as far as I know and he was born in Scotland, he was a Scotsman. But I don't know anything about - all we know - that's all I know, he was a - only son and he used to go to sea. He was seafaring man you see - he used to go to sea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 I thought he worked in the docks?
