No, not my - no, my step-father, he worked in - he used to go to sea - a funny thing he used to go to sea with this - step - with my step-father, you see, they were great friends but - of course he - it was through him having the acci
dent at - not sea, but on shore while he was what they call a doneyman on shore something and he went to go by the hatch 'cos the hatch was open and he fell down the hatch, you see on the -
