eally shocking the way they treated the people them days. I think - I - I don't know. It }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12395442\charrsid2754318 doesn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318  bear to think of your back days really, of what your parents went through to try and - you know - live to - or to help to bring us up. And you see they all got 
