er and he said is Mary in? So she said, yes, why? So he said, could I speak to her? So she said, yes, come in. So she said, Mary, gentleman wants to see you. I said yes. He said, did you have coal money this morning - did you pick up coal money? I said, c
oal money? No, I said, I've never had coal money in my life, I said, never - I said, I've never had any coal money. He said, oh but you did, he said, because your na}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
