 - my girls never had any coal money in her life. So he said, very well, he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4352290\charrsid2754318 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
