\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Was this when you were grown up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 
Yes, when I was about - well, I suppose - well must have been turned thirty then or more you see, this was when my step-father was
 - had a - bad of a - bad turn of no work you see because he told these people that if anything - if he wasn't - if he was at work he didn't mind but if he wasn't at work he'd like me to have had it help you see. So anyway that was that. Time - you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 But before that your father had had a case for compensation?
