l I don't - no, I think she - no, she would - she would - she wouldn't bottle anything but she'd maker her own - her - red cabbage and all that kind of thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 
Pickles and - yes, pickles and - and cabbage and all that, which I've done si
nce she's been gone. I've done all that. Got nice red cabbage and pickled it - cut it up and pickle -'cos she used to show me how to do all this kind of thing you see. Even - with a - with a bloater you see you can open it up the back and take that big bo
n
e out and even with - with eels - with eels you know, she used to skin the eels - lot of people never - don't understand how to skin eels but she wouldn't cook a - eels unless it was skinned. Yes, and she showed me how to do all that. You see, so I suppos
e really that's why I've been able to - I've not been spoilt in any way you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 This is why you've managed so well yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 
Yes, that's what it is because - I often think that if - after I lost my mum you know and if I'd have been spoilt I woul
dn't have known what to cook an egg or anything else would I. I wouldn't have managed to do what I done. No. I couldn't go through that any more. Not now.
\par 
