\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Or medicines for the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Oh well s
he used to make - she used to get some licorice and - linseed and lemon and - and make all that - make that cough mixture - black cough mixture. Doctor Spanish. Doctor Spanish we used to get them days, it used to be lovely. And the linseed and - and the l
e
mon and all that - oh it was lovely. Spanish - Doctor Spanish - get black lumps, big lumps you see well then she'd chop it - bread it up and dissolve it, see, with - with the - with the linseed. Boil all the linseed, strained it - strain it and then she p
ut the lemon in it, you know-oh yes, she - and - every week we used to have - sulphur tablet or licorice powder. Every week she give us a dose of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 She bought those?
