\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10642985\charrsid2754318 thought}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318  of them days was it, n
ot like it is today. I mean it was all fresh wasn't it you see, it was all fresh fruit and stuff.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 You didn't ever keep any livestock?
