Yes. And - once she tried with - with ducks you know. She got ducks eggs and she put seven - she got five ducks eggs. Oh they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10642985\charrsid2754318 gorgeous}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318  things.
