No, she - not while she was in that poor state, we never had meat or any - we just had the bones and the - or except as I say she'd get the little pieces you know, cut them then she'd - wash 'em and stew - do them - make a little meat pie of them you see.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Did you ever have tinned meat?
