r - two. One - the last baby was about two and then the others - two brothers - well, I don't know how old they - one sister and two brothers. That's it - one sister and two brothers you see. Well she - the mother she mother - her mother died when she was
 
thirty-seven. Well she died with T.B. I think and she said to - of course this is what my mother tells me - and she told her, like her - my mum to stand the three children along the wall so that she could see them and she just lifted her head up off the p
