\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2715041 MH  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 That well I don't how she got - she got out anyway - I thin
k her - I think her sister got her out or something, see. Well the got her - her fare to come up to London. - And so anyway she - my aunt would never tell my mother where my father was but she knew where she - where he was you see. And of course eventuall
