 snow white. Well anyway the - the - I don't know who it was but her and this other lady, they got a room between them and they sat - you know, went to - and - and - slept all night you see, and they kept away for two or three days and anyway he found - o
u
t where she was and he brought the children along and he begged and prayed of her to take him back, he wouldn't do it again and all the rest of it. Well I don't know love - after that then she had kids like - she had kids like rabbits. As - as they - she 
