onths or - fourteen months, three years, four years so and so you see well then - every time they died about eleven months well then she'd fall again you see. So - I - I shouldn't say this but I can remember him saying to my mother he said, kids, he said,
 I can't hang me trousers on the end of the bed, he said, that you're not like that. That's awful ain't it. So that's that. That was that. She didn't have a nice life - had a very, very - hard life and she did - she really tried.
