w what I mean. Me. If - if I went say - after doing all the work that I done and I went to the door, you know for a little while and the neighbour next door should be outside she'd say, well - she'd call me in, come on Mary and find something to do. Don't
 stand talking because they're not talking about their own business, they're talking about somebody else and all - that kind of thing you see. So - my - even my life was hard really as well you see.
