ed after her and when she was ill and anybody - my sister came in or - or that and she said, so and so - no, don't you do it, my Mary will do it, my Mary will do it. She wouldn't let anybody do else do, only her Mary. And even when she was in her - dying 
-
 she died - she was dying for a whole week my mother - and - like my sister came, well we 'phoned for her 'cos the doctor said that she wouldn't - she wasn't out of the wood and she wouldn't be. And - she said - I'll never forget as long - it was on a Fri
