own doctor at home and he come and lanced the abscess you see so therefore I didn't go to school see up til I was nearly fourteen. Left before I was fourteen, oh yes. Yes, I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 If you had have been able to would you have liked to have stayed?
