Well I started - I went into cookery and then I learnt - I learnt shorthand and typewrit
ing, I started to learn and - write - reading, writing and arithmetic, see. I went three times a week. Three evenings a week you see so I used to go Mon - Monday, Wednesday and Thursday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Did you go for a long time?
