exam - thorough education and I'd have learnt the piano and all that, you see, I'd have been really educated there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7222989 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12131203\charrsid2754318 Do you think you benefited at all from the education you did have?
